---
---

<section id="tesla" class="bg-ink-elevated/70 border-y border-white/10 py-14 sm:py-16">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 lg:gap-12">
      <div class="lg:w-5/12">
        <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24">
          <div class="uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs text-ember font-semibold mb-2">Tesla · Vision-only</div>
          <h2 class="section-header tracking-tighter mb-4">
            FSD &amp; Cybercab:<br />The Most Ambitious Bet
          </h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
            Tesla relies entirely on cameras and neural nets. This enables faster scaling but creates
            unique challenges.
          </p>

          <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-pulse mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <div><span class="font-medium text-white">13+ billion km</span> of FSD Supervised data.</div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-pulse mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <div>v14 series rolling out; HW3 getting Lite updates in 2026.</div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-pulse mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
              <div>Robotaxi service active in Austin, Dallas, Houston, Miami.</div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:w-7/12 space-y-5">
        <div class="tech-surface p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-start gap-3 mb-5">
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-lg sm:text-xl">Full Self-Driving (Supervised)</div>
              <div class="text-pulse text-sm">Current consumer offering · Level 2</div>
            </div>
            <div class="px-3 py-1 text-xs rounded-2xl bg-emerald-950 text-emerald-400 font-mono self-start">
              v14.x ACTIVE
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3 sm:gap-4 text-sm">
            <div class="bg-ink rounded-2xl p-4 border border-white/5">
              <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500">HW3 / AI3 Vehicles</div>
              <div class="mt-1 font-semibold">v14 Lite rolling out</div>
              <div class="text-[10px] text-amber-400 mt-3">First major update in over a year</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-ink rounded-2xl p-4 border border-white/5">
              <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500">HW4 / AI4 Vehicles</div>
              <div class="mt-1 font-semibold">Full v14 feature set</div>
              <div class="text-[10px] text-emerald-400 mt-3">Improved perception &amp; planning</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-ink rounded-2xl p-4 border border-white/5">
              <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500">Unsupervised</div>
              <div class="mt-1 font-semibold">Target Q4 2026+</div>
              <div class="text-[10px] text-zinc-400 mt-3">Gradual rollout. Safety validation is key hurdle.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-surface overflow-hidden">
          <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="px-3 py-1 bg-ember text-xs font-bold tracking-widest rounded-2xl">CYBERCAB</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-white/60">PURPOSE-BUILT ROBOTAXI</div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-6">
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mb-1">Production (July 2026)</div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-xl sm:text-2xl tracking-tight">Ramping at Giga Texas</div>
                <div class="text-xs mt-2 text-pulse">First unit: Feb 2026 · Volume ramp ongoing</div>

                <dl class="mt-6 text-xs space-y-1.5">
                  <div class="flex justify-between gap-4">
                    <dt class="text-zinc-400">Curb Weight</dt>
                    <dd class="font-mono">3,113 lb</dd>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between gap-4">
                    <dt class="text-zinc-400">Battery</dt>
                    <dd class="font-mono">~48 kWh</dd>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between gap-4">
                    <dt class="text-zinc-400">Powertrain</dt>
                    <dd class="font-mono text-right">FWD single motor, 219 hp</dd>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-between gap-4">
                    <dt class="text-zinc-400">Efficiency</dt>
                    <dd class="font-mono text-pulse">~165 Wh/mi (record)</dd>
                  </div>
                </dl>
              </div>

              <div class="text-sm">
                <div class="mb-3 text-zinc-400">Design Highlights</div>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs">
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-pulse" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> No steering wheel or pedals</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-pulse" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Wireless inductive charging planned</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-pulse" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Self-certification for FMVSS</li>
                  <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-pulse" aria-hidden="true">✓</span> Target &lt; $30k</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="mt-5 p-3 bg-ink rounded-2xl text-xs border-l-2 border-ember">
                  <span class="font-medium text-white">Status:</span> Unsupervised scale still in validation.
                  Current Tesla Robotaxi uses Model Y in geofenced areas.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
